StmtSimple.StatementText: select c.phone_number, c.first_name, c.last_name, c.address_id, a.id, a.line1, a.line2, a.city, a.state, a.zip_code, i.deferred_shipment_date, i.quantity, ic.caption, oc.caption, p.description, s.shipped_on from "order" o join order_item i on i.order_id = o.id left join product p on i.product_id = p.id join customer c on c.id = o.customer_id left join shipment s on s.id = o.shipment_id left join address a on a.id = s.address_id join code oc on oc.id = o.status_code join code ic on ic.id = i.status_code where c.first_name like 'JO%' and c.last_name like 'CO%' and oc.type = 'CLOSED' and ic.type = 'CLOSED' and o.placed > '2017-11-15' order by c.id, o.id desc, s.id, i.id
